  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 7095.81 sitting above the GEX flip at 7071 in PIN regime, dealers are currently long gamma and will sell any rally toward the massive 7200 wall (+7513.6M GEX) while providing buying support on dips toward 7100 (+5002.4M) and especially 7071. The strong positive gamma concentration between 7100-7200 creates a natural range-bound environment where dealer hedging flows will dampen volatility and promote mean reversion. Watch 7071 as the critical level - a break below flips dealers to negative gamma and changes the hedging dynamic entirely.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect price to get pinned between 7100-7200 with dealers capping moves in both directions.",
